description: The SPDR S&P 400 Mid Cap Value ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the S&P MidCap 400 Value Index (the “Index”)The Index includes stocks exhibiting the strongest value characteristics based on: book value to price ratio; earnings to price ratio; and sales to price ratio
name: SPDR S&P 400 Mid Cap Value ETF
